d9ad2ded-61b8-4532-93ea-0b1816fb6668.title: Arhein
d9ad2ded-61b8-4532-93ea-0b1816fb6668.text: Hello! Would you like to trade?

7f131c89-077e-4c8d-aa15-03a90241dbe1.title: Arhein
7f131c89-077e-4c8d-aa15-03a90241dbe1.text:
Yes, I use it to make deliveries to my customers up
and down the coast. These crates here are all ready for
my next trip.

d69a33b1-947a-4cd1-ad5c-3d56ba34b251.title: Arhein
d69a33b1-947a-4cd1-ad5c-3d56ba34b251.text:
Business is going reasonably well... I wouldn't say I
was the richest of merchants ever, but I'm doing fairly
well all things considered.

db2782ad-3d6f-4953-b336-f075c9640124.title: Arhein
db2782ad-3d6f-4953-b336-f075c9640124.text:
Oh, various places up and down the coast. Mostly
Karamja and Port Sarim.

options.text: I don't suppose I could get a lift anywhere?
Well, good luck with your business.

1dabac0a-167e-4981-a2aa-b3fe00db146a.title: <player>
1dabac0a-167e-4981-a2aa-b3fe00db146a.text: Well, good luck with your business.

23e638a4-8bc3-4ce7-b0b9-6a25085f6521.title: <player>
23e638a4-8bc3-4ce7-b0b9-6a25085f6521.text: I don't suppose I could get a lift anywhere?

92af1af0-6920-4411-8b26-ecb927094260.title: Arhein
92af1af0-6920-4411-8b26-ecb927094260.text:
Sorry pal, but I'm afraid I'm not quite ready to sail
yet.

21d08a0d-08e4-4104-b4a5-3d3bfc78c5c7.title: Arhein
21d08a0d-08e4-4104-b4a5-3d3bfc78c5c7.text:
I'm waiting on a big delivery of candles which I need to
deliver further along the coast.
